                   \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Lipari\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/048\">Museo Archeologico Regionale Eoliano \"Luigi Bernabò Brea\"\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003Cidno type=\"inventory\">13677a\u003C/idno>\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\n                                    \u003Cp>Quadrangular stele, well-squared, with smooth surfaces. Gaps along the lower edge; slight chipping on the other edges. The reverse also used for a funerary inscription of later date, same support as \u003Cref sameAs=\"ISic002835.xml\">ISic002835\u003C/ref>.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial type=\"inorganic.stone\" subtype=\"unverified\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/28.html\">volcanic (pietra di Serra)\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.stele\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/250\">stele\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!--ILipara-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">47\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">40.5\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">10.3\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.complete\"/>\n                            \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003C!--Ilipara-->\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"45\" atMost=\"50\">45-50\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462283\">Lipara\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"mo